   This file documents LaTeX, a document preparation system. LaTeX is a
macro package for TeX.

   This is edition 1.1 of the LaTeX documentation, and is for the
Texinfo that is distributed as part of Version 18 of GNU Emacs. It uses
version 2.90 of the texinfo.tex input file.

