_{exp} (subscript)
------------------

   To get an expression @{b}exp@{ub} to appear as a subscript, you just type @{b}
_{exp}@{ub}.  Use in math mode.

   See @{"Math Formulae" Link "Math Formulae"}.

   See @{"Subscripts & Superscripts" Link "Subscripts & Superscripts"}.


@EndNode

