@Toc "List of Commands"

^{exp} (superscript)
--------------------

   To get an expression @{b}exp@{ub} to appear as a superscript, you just type @{b}
^{exp}@{ub}.  Use in math mode.

   See @{"Math Formulae" Link "Math Formulae"}.

   See @{"Subscripts & Superscripts" Link "Subscripts & Superscripts"}.


@EndNode

